; L3: Enemy — wrong-first-push teaching
; Player at (1,2), Box at (4,2), Enemy at (5,2), Goal at (7,2)
; Player walks right into enemy (5,2): denied. Learns they need the box.
; Correct solution: push box LEFT twice to defeat enemy (requires HEAVY face).
; After defeating enemy, player repositions and pushes box RIGHT twice to goal.
; Total: 4 pushes + repositioning. First push is a deny, not a success.

